comment: Flew MJD and around lake. 2 night landings and shot GPS18 into NEW.
Very short flight around pattern to warm engine. Cloud bases ~ 700ft.
Flew to 14M, Hollandale, MS  and back to KNEW with Bobby. Plenty of weather. Great flight to learn about weather and XM weather service.
Round robin, Picayune (KMJD), Wiggins (M24), Lumberton (4R1), Tylertown (T36), Franklinton (4R7), Covington (L31), New Orleans (KNEW). RMM and I went to < 3,000 ft runways. Great time.
New to MJD for fuel. MJD to Yazoo City (87i) @ 65 VFR. 87I to Stennis for the weekend. Fuel @ MJD 42.4, @ HSA 39.2.
4 T&G at NEW on 27. Shot 36 @ HSA.
Round Robin, Stennis, Marion County (0R0), McComb(KMCB), Hammond(KHDC), Lakefront
Nice flight to Bham w/Liz. Flew IFR @ 7,000. Clear, no auto-pilot. Good practice on straight & level by hand!
To Fairhope w/ Rick Blount. 15 minutes IMC. Beechtalk convention.
Back from Faithope w/ Rick Blount. All IMC. GREAT!!
Out to East to check Leroi. AHRS failed on takeoff. Aborted first time then worked, but failed on landing.
To Vicksburg/Tallulah (TVR). Did GAMI test. Beautiful day.
To Ocean Springs and back. Took Harper home.
To Baton Rouge to see Liz and the Bohns. Dinner at Chris'. Fun.
From KNEW to KECP. Nice flight.
CQF back to ECP. SHOT ILS 16 into ECP. Problem with ILS capturing localizer & glideslope.
ECP to CQF for annual at Continental FBO.
Annual inspection at Continental Motors Fairhope. Cost 7,385.46.
Back from LCH. IMC 20 minutes. Shot ILS18 into NEW. Great flight.
Around shell beach, then up to MJD for fuel.
Flew Harper home and returned New Orleans with Merrick. At night. Fun!
To: MJD for fuel. Oil came up to 12.5 after sitting for a month!
Flew to Athens with Nina and Bobby. Great flight, cold as hell though.
Back from Athens with Monsted. Great flying day.
To Albany w/Liz to shoot quail at Nochaway Plantation. What a ball!
Flew practice approaches with Beron. HSA, MJD, ASD, HDC, L10, NEW and hold.
To KAHN Nina parents weekend. Great flight.
Flight back from Athens with Liz. Easy flight, CAVU, but big headwinds. Left Tip Tanks 1/2 full.
To Albany with Liz. Weather tricky. 20 min IMC.
Flight to Albany to shoot quail with the Slosses and Melanee and Jay Grenny
Flew in scud to 0R0, 4R1, MJD, home. Lot's weather. Pop up IFR clearance and GPS 23 approach at 0R0.
New-Btr-PTN-HUM-NEW. With Bobby. A ball and clear day.
BHAM for lunch with Petie. Liz came. Good trip.
To Acadiana Regional with Rick Blount to see Tia II, 53' Hatteras belonging to Tony Simmons. Great boat and shot GPS 16 at AYA  and got instrument time.
To CLT to see Buzz and Patty. Great flight.
Flew CLT - AVL. DP Hugo2, 270d to SUG direct AVL @ 8,000ft. Nice flight.
AVL - NEW. Very nice at 8,000. Weather at NEW, flew ILS 18R. Tips are empty.
To Ocean Springs and back for Harper with Merrick.
To Athens to pick up Nina and Meredith Marmonde with Monsted.
AHN to 4R3 for fuel, then on to NEW with Nina Meredith and Bobby.
To picayune with Monty and Julie with Liz to a party at Christovich's house. Very nice day.
To HSA, shot GPS 18 w/ hold, MJD, GPS 18 w/vectors to final. Thomas Beron safety pilot.
New to Austin Executive. Very nice airport. Gas expensive.
KEDC to Marfa. Bumpy at the end of the flight. But fun.
Marfa to St John's Industrial Airpark. Nice flight. RMM, PM, EHS, LRS.
St Johns to Grand Canyon. Very high DA. Long takeoff run.
Grand Canyon to Santa Fe. Great flight at 11,000. Plane climbed very well leaned to DA AT takeoff.
Kickapoo to NOLa. Very smooth and nice flight.
To EFD with Liz and Nina. Great flight. Shot ILS 17R into Ellington Field. ILS didn't pick up signal until late in approach.
Back to NEW from EFD @ 70. Lot's of weather to go around. Good practice.
Shot HSA ILS18, MJD GPS 18, NEW ILS 18 w/ r. Monsted safety pilot.
NEW-HSA-MJD-NEW, GPS 18@HSA, MJD, GPS 36@NEW, HOLD @HSA W/Rick Blount.
Flew around lake w/Bobby and little Bobby.
To Fairhope for work on exhaust stack
New Orleans back to Fairhope after plane returned by Continental
Fairhope after dropping off Sean fm Continental
To Watercolor with Liz. CAVU. Great flight
Down beach in Watercolor with Thomas V and Doug G. A ball.
ECP-NEW return from Watercolor. Great day and trip.
to MJD for GPS 18 w/hold, vfr 18, ILS 18r @NEW, 3 night landings
To Fairhope and back to pick up Sean for annual.
Fairhope to NEW. Sean returned plane to CQF.
Eagle Lake with Merrick and Bobby Monsted
Down river with Christy. Fun day
To MJD VOR-A w/hold, GPS36, VOR-A again.
To Albany to hunt Nochaway with the Jones CAVU @ 90. Great Trip.
Back from KABY. Very nice flight at 60.
KNEW to PNS for BFR and IPC w/ Al Malone
To MJD w/ RMM shot VOR A twice
To MJD for fuel. Shot VOR-A and GPS 18. Solo.
to Ocean Springs to pick up Harper.
W/RMM to PIB, MJD shot GPS 18, then NEW.
To ECP w/JGP. A little bumpy but beautiful. Lbase for 34, wind howling.
Back from ECP solo. Very windy and cloudy. Shot ILS 18R at NEW.
To MJD practiced GPS 36, touch and go, went missed, then back to NEW.
to MJD w/RMM. GPS 36 and hold.
To BHM w/EHS. Nice flight, bumpy last 1/2 hour.
Back to NEW w/EHS. Very nice, smooth flight.
To RMM's daughter's house near Hattiesburg.  Shot GPS 18 at BXA. Then to KNEW.
JML LRS flew over kiln property and down river.
To CQF for AD on yoke and fuel safety stop. Also, check steering; not  enough left.
Back from CQF; lots of weather. A ball.
w/RMM to MS delta to look for duck camps.
up to Slidell for fuel. Autopilot broke.

Diamondhead for 4 landings. practiced short field take offs, 
1 T & G at HSA and back to KNEW for 090 landing.
to 0R0, MJD, practiced slow flight, stalls w/ RMM.
To MJD, slow flight, stalls, shot GPS18, flew missed, landed, fuel. To KNEW shot ILS18. W/RMM.
To Greenville (KGLH) w/RMM & Sartor to look at duck properties.
To MJD for fuel. Filled tips.
to AVL w/EHS. Great flight, quick time.
Back from Charleston w/Liz. Weather was ok but forecast was convective.
To NEW fm AVL. Lot's of weater to avoid. 15 min inst.
W/RMM, shot L38 GPS 35, HDC 36, MJD Hold & Dead Stick landing, MJD GPS 36 w/Hold.
To MCB - GPS 33 w hold, 0R0 - GPS 23, MJD VOR-A w/dead stick landing. RMM safety pilot #1949466
to MJD for VOR-A. Practiced 3 dead stick landings, then to NEW.
VOR practice holding. Also, dead stick.
to KGLH to meet with duck camp people. RMM, HBF, OS.
back from Greenville. Lots of IMC. 30 minutes.
to MJD for lunch with McCarthy, Burl, Christo. Then downriver to MSM's camp and back up to NEW.
Flew holds at OYSTY for 1.2 hours with Monsted.
